ing: salt and ground black pepper to taste
des: "Real light and refreshing either as starter or side salad. Easily doubles. I have used Parmesan instead of Asiago cheese. Nuts can be left out. I have also used pecans."
ins: Combine spinach, almonds, onion, and Asiago cheese in a large bowl. Drizzle dressing over salad and season with salt and pepper. Add peaches and toss.
